1
00:00:02,23 --> 00:00:04,72
Phoebe found out about this lady...
我们跑去海边 因为菲比找到一个女人

2
00:00:04,93 --> 00:00:09,03
...who knew her parents, and I don't know what happened.
她认识她的父母 然后我就不知道了

3
00:00:09,30 --> 00:00:10,90
I'm your mother.
我是你的母亲

4
00:00:11,64 --> 00:00:14,77
Monica joked she wouldn't date Chandler.
摩妮卡开玩笑说 她不会跟钱德这种人约会

5
00:00:14,98 --> 00:00:17,88
I don't know what happened there either.
他一直很在意 然后我也不知道了

6
00:00:18,08 --> 00:00:20,31
Ross' new girlfriend shows up.
罗斯的新女朋友邦妮跑来

7
00:00:20,55 --> 00:00:24,45
Rachel gets Bonnie to shave her head. Then they kiss.
瑞秋说服她理了个大光头 然后罗斯和瑞秋接吻了

8
00:00:24,65 --> 00:00:27,82
Now he has to choose Rachel or the bald girl.
现在他得在瑞秋 和光头女之间二选一

9
00:00:28,16 --> 00:00:30,25
I don't know what happened there either.
然后我还是不知道

10
00:00:30,46 --> 00:00:32,93
Hold on. Let me go get Chandler.
等一下，我去找钱德来

11
00:00:49,98 --> 00:00:52,61
She's helping me. My head's sunburned.
她在帮我搽药，我的头晒伤了

12
00:00:55,52 --> 00:00:58,82
-Thanks a million. -You're welcome a million.
感激不尽 不用客气

13
00:00:59,02 --> 00:01:00,99
Smell it.
你闻

14
00:01:03,59 --> 00:01:05,62
Minty.
凉凉的

15
00:01:06,96 --> 00:01:09,05
I'll be in our room.
我先回房去

16
00:01:23,48 --> 00:01:24,67
Oh,my God!
天哪

17
00:01:24,88 --> 00:01:26,37
I know.
我知道

18
00:01:30,15 --> 00:01:31,52
I got to go.
好，我走了

19
00:01:32,25 --> 00:01:33,28
Why?
什么？为什么？

20
00:01:33,42 --> 00:01:36,05
I got to go break up with Bonnie.
我得跟邦妮分手

21
00:01:36,66 --> 00:01:38,22
Here? Now?
在这里？现在？

22
00:01:38,46 --> 00:01:40,29
I can't stay here all night.
我不能整晚留在这里

23
00:01:40,56 --> 00:01:43,40
If I go in there,she'll want to...
要是我回房，她会想…

24
00:01:44,10 --> 00:01:45,09
...do stuff.
嘿咻

25
00:01:46,30 --> 00:01:49,00
Can't you say you aren't in the mood?
你不能说你没心情吗？

26
00:01:49,17 --> 00:01:50,66
No,she likes that.
她喜欢那样

27
00:01:52,64 --> 00:01:54,37
Faking sleep doesn't work.
装睡也没用

28
00:01:54,64 --> 00:01:57,20
I've woken up many times with her
我经常早上醒来发现她在…

29
00:01:57,35 --> 00:01:58,33
好

30
00:02:00,08 --> 00:02:03,05
-Why am I telling you? -I don't know.
我说这个干什么？ 我不知道

31
00:02:12,26 --> 00:02:15,29
-Not every morning -Making it worse!
并不是每天早上都… 再描会更黑

32
00:02:16,76 --> 00:02:18,66
The One with the Jellyfish
本集播出：“前缘难续”

00:02:21,66 --> 00:02:23,66
rainystar压制iPod-MP4

33
00:03:04,41 --> 00:03:07,38
You probably want to know how it happened.
你大概想知道前因后果

34
00:03:07,65 --> 00:03:10,08
I think I can figure it out.
我猜想得到

35
00:03:10,35 --> 00:03:14,15
I was born,and then everyone lied their asses off.
我出生之后 大家开始卯起来撒谎

36
00:03:14,89 --> 00:03:17,36
No,it wasn't like that.
不是那样的

37
00:03:17,69 --> 00:03:21,18
Remember how I said Lilly,Frank and I were close?
我不是说过 莉莉、法兰克和我很要好？

38
00:03:22,46 --> 00:03:24,02
We were very close.
我们非常要好

39
00:03:24,30 --> 00:03:25,66
How close?
怎么说？

40
00:03:25,87 --> 00:03:29,46
The three of us were kind of a couple.
我们三个是一对

41
00:03:31,31 --> 00:03:33,74
I don't know how that would work.
三个怎么会是一对

42
00:03:33,94 --> 00:03:35,03
I'm not asking!
我们… 我不是在问你

43
00:03:36,41 --> 00:03:38,94
Anyhow,somehow I got pregnant...
总之，我不知怎的怀孕了

44
00:03:39,65 --> 00:03:41,14
...and I was...
我很…

45
00:03:41,62 --> 00:03:45,11
...scared. I was stupid and selfish....
…害怕，我愚昧又自私…

46
00:03:45,99 --> 00:03:50,45
I was 18 years old. Remember what it was like to be 18?
我才18岁 还记得你的18岁吗？

47
00:03:50,66 --> 00:03:53,49
Mom killed herself and my dad ran off.
记得，妈自杀，爸跑掉

48
00:03:53,73 --> 00:03:57,66
I lived in a Gremlin with a guy who talked to his hand.
我跟一个叫山迪的人住在一起 他会跟他的手说话

49
00:03:59,90 --> 00:04:04,34
I'm sorry. I thought I'd left you with the best parents.
对不起 我以为他们是世上最好的父母

50
00:04:04,51 --> 00:04:07,37
I didn't hear about them till a few years ago.
直到几年前 我才听说他们的事

51
00:04:07,64 --> 00:04:09,80
By then,you were already grown-up.
当时你已经长大了

52
00:04:09,98 --> 00:04:14,57
You're here and I would really like to get to know you.
既然你来了，我也想多认识你

53
00:04:14,75 --> 00:04:16,65
Well,everybody does.
每个人都想认识我

54
00:04:17,92 --> 00:04:19,94
I'm a really cool person.
我是个很酷的人

55
00:04:20,26 --> 00:04:24,12
You had 29 years to find out, but you didn't even try.
你有29年的时间可以查 却连试都没试

56
00:04:25,43 --> 00:04:28,52
You walked out on me, and I'll do the same.
你扔下我不管，现在我也要

57
00:04:29,53 --> 00:04:32,02
I don't ever want to see you again.
等一下

58
00:04:29,76 --> 00:04:31,53
我不想再见到你

59
00:04:36,00 --> 00:04:37,94
Where's my purse?
我的皮包呢？

60
00:04:39,84 --> 00:04:41,83
Shoot! We're out of soda.
讨厌，没有汽水了

61
00:04:42,11 --> 00:04:44,44
-I'll get you some. -Really?
我去帮你买 真的？

62
00:04:44,61 --> 00:04:47,01
No,because I'm not your boyfriend.
才怪，我又不是你的男朋友

63
00:04:49,05 --> 00:04:50,95
Hey,Pheebs,how'd it go?
菲比，怎么样？

65
00:04:53,49 --> 00:04:56,92
My mom's friend,Phoebe, is actually my birth mom.
我妈的朋友菲比 其实是我的亲生母亲

66
00:05:00,33 --> 00:05:02,66
I found a dried-up seahorse.
我检到一个干掉的海马

67
00:05:03,67 --> 00:05:05,10
What do you mean?
什么意思？

68
00:05:05,30 --> 00:05:08,27
My new mom, who's a big fat abandoner.
我的新妈妈当年抛弃了我

69
00:05:09,80 --> 00:05:13,24
Don't you want to stay here and talk about it?
菲比，等等 你不坐下来聊一聊吗？

71
00:05:15,21 --> 00:05:16,97
I need to be alone.
不了，我想静一静

72
00:05:20,11 --> 00:05:21,38
摩妮卡

73
00:05:27,06 --> 00:05:29,05
Man. Hey...

74
00:05:29,19 --> 00:05:32,52
...what if you found out that your mom wasn't really your mom...
要是你发现你妈不是你妈

75
00:05:32,66 --> 00:05:36,36
...and your new mom turned out to be really hot?
而你的新妈妈又很辣呢？

76
00:05:36,50 --> 00:05:39,40
Oh,man,huh?

77
00:05:40,54 --> 00:05:43,27
But,it's your mom.
但她是你妈耶

78
00:05:43,40 --> 00:05:46,93
No,I'm talking about your mom.
不，我是在说你妈

79
00:05:55,82 --> 00:05:56,84
It's over.
结束了

80
00:05:58,42 --> 00:06:00,08
Was it awful?
很惨吗？

81
00:06:00,25 --> 00:06:01,74
It was long.
很久

82
00:06:02,52 --> 00:06:04,62
I didn't realize how late it was...
我没意识到那么晚了

83
00:06:04,83 --> 00:06:07,85
...till I saw the five o'clock shadow on her head.
直到她头上出现5点钟的日影

84
00:06:13,27 --> 00:06:17,33
She didn't want to stay. I called a cab. She just left.
她不想留下来 我帮她叫了车，她刚走

85
00:06:25,01 --> 00:06:27,00
I wrote you a letter.
我写了封信给你

86
00:06:27,28 --> 00:06:29,11
Oh,thank you!
谢谢

87
00:06:30,22 --> 00:06:32,02
I like mail.
我喜欢收信

88
00:06:36,29 --> 00:06:40,42
It's just some things I've been thinking about. About us.
我想了一些关于我们的事

89
00:06:40,66 --> 00:06:44,10
Before we even think about us getting back together...
在我们考虑复合之前

90
00:06:44,33 --> 00:06:47,39
...I need to know how you feel about this stuff.
我得知道你对这封信的想法

91
00:06:50,20 --> 00:06:51,50
好

92
00:06:57,88 --> 00:07:00,01
It's 5:30 in the morning.
现在是早上5点半

93
00:07:02,88 --> 00:07:06,34
So I'd better get cracking on this baby.
我最好赶快看完

94
00:07:09,19 --> 00:07:11,45
I'll be waiting for you. Come up when you're done.
我等你，看完就上来

95
00:07:12,56 --> 00:07:14,53
I'll be up...
好，我要花…

96
00:07:15,36 --> 00:07:16,83
...in 18 pages.
十八页的时间

97
00:07:19,00 --> 00:07:20,30
Front and back.
从头到尾

98
00:07:22,17 --> 00:07:24,00
Very exciting!
好兴奋喔

99
00:07:50,03 --> 00:07:52,50
What happened to you? Why didn't you come up?
怎么了？你怎么没上来？

100
00:07:53,20 --> 00:07:54,33
Done.
看完了

101
00:07:56,14 --> 00:07:59,37
-You just finished? -I wanted to be thorough.
你才刚看完？ 我想看仔细一点

102
00:08:00,07 --> 00:08:05,24
This is clearly very important to you. To us.
这对你…对我们显然很重要

103
00:08:05,41 --> 00:08:09,18
I wanted to read every word carefully.
我想一字一句用心斟酌

104
00:08:09,38 --> 00:08:11,65
Twice.
斟酌两次

106
00:08:14,99 --> 00:08:16,92
Does it?
所以…行吗？

107
00:08:22,36 --> 00:08:24,30
I'm sorry?
什么？

108
00:08:25,53 --> 00:08:27,13
Does it?
行吗？

109
00:08:28,27 --> 00:08:32,33
Does it? Does it?
行吗？行吗？

110
00:08:35,14 --> 00:08:39,81
I wanted to give that whole "Does it?" part another glance.
我想再瞄一眼“行吗”的部份

111
00:08:39,98 --> 00:08:43,08
What do you mean? You said you read it twice.
什么意思？你说你看了两次

112
00:08:43,35 --> 00:08:46,95
It either does or doesn't. If you have to think
行不行一句话 如果你还要考虑…

113
00:08:47,19 --> 00:08:50,45
No,I don't have to think about it.
不，我不用考虑，不用

114
00:08:50,66 --> 00:08:51,92
In fact...
事实上…

115
00:08:52,69 --> 00:08:55,42
...I've decided. I have decided...
我已经决定了，我决定…

116
00:08:55,93 --> 00:08:57,59
...that it...
这件事…

117
00:09:03,10 --> 00:09:04,47
...does.
行

118
00:09:21,29 --> 00:09:24,19
-Are you sure? -Sure,I'm sure!
你确定？ 确定

119
00:09:31,47 --> 00:09:35,63
There's a nuclear holocaust. I'm the last man on earth.
好，发生核爆灾难 我是世上仅存的男人

120
00:09:36,00 --> 00:09:38,20
Would you go out with me?
你会跟我约会吗？

121
00:09:43,51 --> 00:09:45,95
I've got canned goods.
我有罐头喔

122
00:09:46,98 --> 00:09:49,07
Take a look at this!
喂，你们看

123
00:09:49,32 --> 00:09:52,45
Check this baby out! Dug me a hole.
你们瞧瞧，我挖了个洞

124
00:09:54,52 --> 00:09:56,58
Excellent hole,Joe.
好棒的洞啊

125
00:09:58,29 --> 00:10:00,59
Oh,no! My hole!
不！我的洞！

126
00:10:00,76 --> 00:10:02,25
My foot!
我的脚！

127
00:10:03,30 --> 00:10:04,42
What is it?
怎么了？

128
00:10:04,80 --> 00:10:07,93
Jellyfish sting! It hurts!
我被水母咬了，好痛…

129
00:10:08,20 --> 00:10:10,19
Can we help you to the house?
要不要扶你回去？

130
00:10:10,40 --> 00:10:11,74
It's two miles.
2哩耶

131
00:10:11,94 --> 00:10:14,20
And I'm tired from digging.
而且我挖洞挖得好累

132
00:10:15,78 --> 00:10:17,54
Damn the jellyfish!
该死的水母

133
00:10:17,78 --> 00:10:20,25
Damn all the jellyfish!
所有的水母都去死

134
00:10:20,45 --> 00:10:21,75
Do something.
得想个办法

135
00:10:21,98 --> 00:10:23,45
There's only one thing.
只有一个办法

136
00:10:23,65 --> 00:10:24,74
What is it?
什么办法？

137
00:10:24,99 --> 00:10:26,25
Pee on it.
在伤口上撒尿

138
00:10:29,09 --> 00:10:30,08
Gross!
什么？好恶！

139
00:10:30,32 --> 00:10:32,49
I saw it on Discovery Channel.
别怪我 我是在探索频道上看到的

140
00:10:32,79 --> 00:10:36,13
He's right. There's ammonia in that...
他没唬你，尿液里有氨

141
00:10:36,80 --> 00:10:38,16
...that kills the pain.
可以止痛

142
00:10:38,43 --> 00:10:42,30
Forget it. It doesn't hurt that bad!
我不要，其实没那么痛…

143
00:10:43,50 --> 00:10:45,40
You can use my hole for privacy.
你可以躲进我的洞里

144
00:10:48,98 --> 00:10:52,14
I'm ready to get the hell out of here.
我准备好要走了

145
00:10:54,62 --> 00:10:55,78
Are you?
你们…？真的？

146
00:10:57,52 --> 00:10:59,42
That's so great!
太棒了

147
00:10:59,75 --> 00:11:00,91
Not for Bonnie.
邦妮好可怜

148
00:11:02,89 --> 00:11:04,45
But for you,yea!
但恭喜你们了

149
00:11:06,49 --> 00:11:09,83
-How was the beach? -Nothing. I don't know.
海边好玩吗？ 不怎么样，我不知道

150
00:11:12,53 --> 00:11:14,50
-What happened? -Nothing.
怎么了？ 没事

151
00:11:14,70 --> 00:11:17,17
-I'm going to shower. -Me too.
我要去冲澡 我也是

152
00:11:17,44 --> 00:11:18,63
Me too.
我也是

153
00:11:19,94 --> 00:11:21,60
I'll put this in the car.
我把袋子拿到车上

154
00:11:21,84 --> 00:11:24,00
I have to go pack!
我得去收东西

155
00:11:25,38 --> 00:11:28,01
-And it really does? -lt does.
真的行吗？ 行

156
00:11:28,22 --> 00:11:30,31
It really and truly does.
真的真的行

157
00:11:53,01 --> 00:11:55,81
It so does not!
行你个头！

158
00:11:59,71 --> 00:12:01,68
（中央咖啡馆）

159
00:12:01,92 --> 00:12:06,44
She wants me to take responsibility for everything that went wrong.
她要我对我们的失和 负起全部的责任

160
00:12:07,09 --> 00:12:11,92
She goes on for five pages about how I was unfaithful to her.
她写了整整五页 说我如何不忠

161
00:12:12,63 --> 00:12:15,22
We were on a break!
我们当时分手了

162
00:12:15,50 --> 00:12:19,66
If you say that one more time, I'll break up with you.
天哪，你再说一次 我就跟你分手

163
00:12:21,07 --> 00:12:24,73
This breakup was not all my fault. She says here...
分手不是我一个人的错 她写说

164
00:12:25,04 --> 00:12:27,84
..."lf you accept full responsibility...
“要是你负起全部的责任”

165
00:12:28,04 --> 00:12:30,57
...I can begin to trust you again.
“我就能再次信任你”

166
00:12:30,78 --> 00:12:34,44
Does that seem like something you can do? Does it?"
“你想你办得到吗？行吗？”

167
00:12:37,15 --> 00:12:38,98
不行

168
00:12:39,79 --> 00:12:43,05
You have what you want. You're back with her.
你得偿所愿，跟她复合了

169
00:12:43,29 --> 00:12:46,23
If you bring this up now, you'll wreck it.
现在提出来 会毁了你一生中最美好的事

170
00:12:46,53 --> 00:12:48,86
Yeah,I know. You're right.
我知道，你说得对

171
00:12:51,13 --> 00:12:52,33
I'll let it go.
我会就此打住

172
00:12:52,63 --> 00:12:55,80
But you know how hard it is to forget this?
但你们了解这件事很难忘记吧

173
00:12:56,07 --> 00:12:57,63
Sure,it's hard...
当然很难

174
00:12:57,91 --> 00:13:00,64
...but you don't have to talk about it.
但你不必拿出来谈

175
00:13:01,54 --> 00:13:03,94
A lot happened on that trip...
这次度假有很多事 

176
00:13:04,15 --> 00:13:07,31
...that we should never,ever talk about.
都该从此绝口不提

177
00:13:09,92 --> 00:13:12,11
What happened on that beach?
在海边到底怎么了？

178
00:13:13,82 --> 00:13:16,81
It's between us and the sea,Ross.
那是我们和大海的秘密

179
00:13:26,40 --> 00:13:27,80
Hi,Ursula.
乌苏拉

180
00:13:29,24 --> 00:13:32,83
I know that we haven't talked in a long time.
我知道我们很久没联络了

181
00:13:33,14 --> 00:13:37,87
Our mom is not our birth mom. This other lady is our birth mom.
但我们的妈妈不是亲妈妈 另一个女的才是

182
00:13:38,11 --> 00:13:41,24
Right,the one that lives in Montauk.
对，住在莫陶克的那个

183
00:13:41,72 --> 00:13:42,70
You know her?
你认识她？

184
00:13:42,98 --> 00:13:46,71
No. I read about her in Mom's suicide note.
不认识，但妈的遗书里有提到

185
00:13:46,99 --> 00:13:51,22
There was a suicide note? Do you still have it?
妈有留遗书？还在吗？

186
00:13:52,16 --> 00:13:53,75
Hang on.
等一下

187
00:13:56,10 --> 00:13:59,03
I can't believe you didn't tell me there was a suicide note.
你居然没告诉我有遗书

188
00:13:59,30 --> 00:14:01,50
Yeah,so how have you been doing?
是啊，你最近好吗？

189
00:14:02,84 --> 00:14:04,13
Shut up!
我…闭嘴

190
00:14:08,64 --> 00:14:11,34
"Goodbye,Phoebe and Ursula. I'll miss you.
“别了，菲比与乌苏拉” “我会想念你们”

191
00:14:11,55 --> 00:14:14,04
P.S. Your mom lives in Montauk."
“又：你们母亲住在莫陶克”

